{"tid":662383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"55%受訪醫生反佔中　少於一半醫生支持公民提名特首候選人","createTime":"2018-05-12T11:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T17:32:40.000Z","uid":19552,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bc7a1238423488b028955d34ccaf9ead7e2ca500","tid":662383,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"香港醫學會剛公布，上月底問卷調查約1500名註冊西醫及牙醫對往後普選進程的看法。據報道，49%受訪者贊成應該有公民提名，但有55%反對佔領中環。當中醫學會會長謝鴻興表明，他個人反對公民提名，認為不符《基本法》；前會長蔡堅指，醫生多不習慣參與靜坐抗議，有醫生更怕若參加佔中違法行動，會影響執照。副會長周伯展則更指，有醫生擔心佔中會癱瘓中環，影響病人到他們的中環診所求診。<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都同意，本地醫學界的政治取向，代表了部分本港專業人士的看法；至於周伯展提出的有醫生怕佔中會影響他們中環診所的運作，姑勿論是站在病人角度還是診所業務著想，曾經是行政長官梁振英親密戰友的前全國政協委員劉夢熊曾說過，周伯展本人在2012年5月梁振英準備出任新一任特首前，就曾獲梁振英設家宴招待。此後亦盛傳，周伯展是梁振英的醫學界智囊，並在去年7月1日獲委為太平紳士。"},{"pid":"a9bc40e5bea0c99d6454ab5aa1ba8a6d30a6bddc","tid":662383,"uid":24296,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:15:51.000Z","msg":"有醫生擔心佔中會癱瘓中環，影響病人到他們的中環診所求診。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c2039b82439953ee0959cb99cf346c669d940b","tid":662383,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ac895751421082b622b099a2350cf5c7b2f84c","tid":662383,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c9cccfb4505fe17d172425434acdedbf0926ba7","tid":662383,"uid":37733,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T15:16:01.000Z","msg":"人地唔想同d佔中地底泥玩洗牌"},{"pid":"283e5ac41740e9574fe72c339f50636881d44b33","tid":662383,"uid":47005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"班醫生好多都離地中產黎架"},{"pid":"d96cc6b6aa57bc3115863e81b0b69da1002107ff","tid":662383,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba9b0e4a2d542023c4a86024d37cd18b0914d67","tid":662383,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:18:34.000Z","msg":"得閒反支，不如諗下點sell貴價療法/貴價保健藥/全身檢查比支那人好過"},{"pid":"03a61bddf1c75b07da18608a230affab56f3f2fd","tid":662383,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"得55%反係咪算少<br />\n唔知其他行業係幾多<br />\n零售業應該100%反<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d452f4f254f921a6befb089d15e4b45094745e8b","tid":662383,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:32:40.000Z","msg":"【醫學界政改民調 過半數反對831 | 港聞】<br />\n<br />\n立法會醫學界議員梁家騮公佈醫學界政改民意調查結果，共收回超過三千份回覆，有五成半人認為，立法會應否決按831框架製訂的2017年政改方案，近四成半人支持通過方案。<br />\n<br />\n詳文 <a href=\"http://goo.gl/63Egpi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F63Egpi&d=QLLjAeUuz8vvragMMw%2FMP54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=76240f80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/63Egpi</a><br />\n<br />\n#謎米港聞<br />\n<br />\n謎米新聞．呼吸新聞空氣 <a href=\"http://news.memehk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com&d=QLLjAeUuz8vvragMMw%2FMP54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=377375b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">news.memehk.com</a>"}]}